TopicTitle: [KSP 1.8.1] Can't launch vessels big vessels in science mode

Articles.Content:
Whenever I switch SPH and VAB, I'm unable to build large vessels.

 

To reproduce:

- Load game in science or sandbox mode

- Go to SPH or VAB

- Switch editors until both mass and size are limited
